Example data for MetNet: unit tests

mat_test.Rd

mat_test contains 7 toy features that were derived from rnorm. It will be used as an example data set in unit tests.

Format

matrix

Source

set.seed(1) random_numbers <- rnorm(140, mean = 10, sd = 2) mat_test <- matrix(random_numbers, nrow = 7) mat_test[1:3, ] <- t(apply(mat_test[1:3, ], 1, sort)) mat_test[5:7, ] <- t(apply(mat_test[5:7, ], 1, sort, decreasing = TRUE)) rownames(mat_test) <- paste("x", 1:7, sep = "")

Value

matrix
